Man with Sword Takes Two Hostages on Train in France, Sky Says

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-07-06T19:32:55Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-06/man-with-sword-takes-two-hostages-on-train-in-france-sky-says.html
A 25-year old man carrying a sword
has taken two hostages on a train in  Bordeaux ,  France , Sky News
reported, without attribution. Police are negotiating with the
hostage-taker, and 15 people have been let go, Sky said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Blanche Gatt in London at 
 bgatt@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Colin Keatinge at 
 ckeatinge@bloomberg.net . 